OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778097967
OL,3,CMcCann family MP wants suspect in
OL,4,CMadeleine's disappearance to face
OL,5,Ctrial in UK
OL,7,FThe MP for Madeleine McCann's family
OL,8,Fis calling for the prime suspect in
OL,9,Ftheir daughter's disappearance to be
OL,10,Fextradited to the UK, if sufficient
OL,11,Fevidence is in place to bring him to
OL,12,Ftrial.
OL,14,FPeter Bedford, the MP for Mid
OL,15,FLeicestershire, said the McCann
OL,16,Ffamily, from Rothley, need closure.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778097967
OL,3,CMcCann family MP wants suspect in
OL,4,CMadeleine's disappearance to face
OL,5,Ctrial in UK
OL,7,FHe added that the German government
OL,8,Fneed to "listen to the case put
OL,9,Fforward by prosecutors" so that "an
OL,10,Fextradition arraignment can be put
OL,11,Finto place" for the prime suspect
OL,12,FChristian Brueckner.
OL,14,FMadeline McCann disappeared in May
OL,15,F2007 while on holiday in Portugal. She
OL,16,Fwas left in an apartment with her
OL,17,Fyounger siblings as their parents went
OL,18,Fout to dinner with friends.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
