OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778097967
OL,3,CMcCann family MP wants suspect in
OL,4,CMadeleine's disappearance to face
OL,5,Ctrial in UK
OL,7,FChristian Brueckner has been the main
OL,8,Fsuspect in the Madeline McCann case
OL,9,Ffor four years after he was formally
OL,10,Fnamed by German police in 2022.
OL,12,FThis comes as the Met Police is
OL,13,Freportedly pushing to bring Brueckner
OL,14,Fto the UK to stand trial.
OL,16,FDetectives are said to be pressing for
OL,17,Fa German national to be extradited to
OL,18,FBritain, as it is reported that they
OL,19,Fcan gather enough evidence for the
OL,20,FCrown Prosecution Service to charge
OL,21,Fhim for abduction and murder.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778097967
OL,3,CMcCann family MP wants suspect in
OL,4,CMadeleine's disappearance to face
OL,5,Ctrial in UK
OL,7,FThis might be complicated because
OL,8,FArticle 26 of the German constitution
OL,9,Fstops any citizen from being
OL,10,Fextradited to a non-EU country.
OL,12,FBritain and Germany do have a
OL,13,Freciprocal extradition agreement that
OL,14,Fcame into force in 2021, but Germany
OL,15,Fcan still block it.
OL,17,FA Met spokesperson said: "The Met's
OL,18,Finvestigation into the disappearance
OL,19,Fof Madeleine McCann has been active
OL,20,Fsince 2011.
OL,26,@yD@ZOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/11
