PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778097967
OL,3,CMcCann family MP wants suspect in
OL,4,CMadeleine's disappearance to face
OL,5,Ctrial in UK
OL,7,F"A dedicated team continues to examine
OL,8,Fthe events of the evening of 3 May
OL,9,F2007 in Praia da Luz, while supporting
OL,10,Fand updating Madeleine's family.
OL,12,F"As part of ongoing enquiries, we
OL,13,Fremain in close working discussion
OL,14,Fwith policing colleagues in Germany
OL,15,Fand Portugal.
OL,17,F"We will continue to pursue any viable
OL,18,Flines of enquiry."
OL,20,FWho is Christian Brueckner?
OL,26,@tD@AOUzD@RO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778097967
OL,3,CMcCann family MP wants suspect in
OL,4,CMadeleine's disappearance to face
OL,5,Ctrial in UK
OL,7,FChristian Brueckner has been the main
OL,8,Fsuspect in the Madeline McCann case
OL,9,Ffor four years, but has always denied
OL,10,Fany involvement.
OL,12,FBrueckner lived in the Portuguese
OL,13,Fcoastal village of Praia da Luz on and
OL,14,Foff between 1995 and 2007, and was
OL,15,Fbased around a mile away from the
OL,16,Fresort where the McCanns were staying.
OL,18,FBrueckner was released from a German
OL,19,Fprison last year after serving seven
OL,20,Fyears for raping a woman.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778097967
OL,3,CMcCann family MP wants suspect in
OL,4,CMadeleine's disappearance to face
OL,5,Ctrial in UK
OL,7,FThe German national, also known as
OL,8,FChristian B, was imprisoned for the
OL,9,Frape of a 72-year-old US woman in
OL,10,FPraia da Luz in Portugal, in 2005.
OL,12,FHe also has two previous convictions
OL,13,Ffor sexual abuse of a child, in
OL,14,Funrelated cases to Madeleine McCann.
OL,16,FBrueckner has never been charged in
OL,17,Frelation to the McCann case, but
OL,18,FGerman authorities began investigating
OL,19,Fhim in June 2020 for her kidnap and
OL,20,Fmurder.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
