OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778097967
OL,3,CMcCann family MP wants suspect in
OL,4,CMadeleine's disappearance to face
OL,5,Ctrial in UK
OL,7,FThe most recent search took place in
OL,8,FJune last year, when German and
OL,9,FPortuguese investigators focused on a
OL,10,Fnumber of abandoned buildings in the
OL,11,Fcountryside near Praia da Luz, between
OL,12,Fthe complex and where Christian
OL,13,FBrueckner had been staying.
OL,15,FThe search ended with no significant
OL,16,Fbreakthroughs.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
