PN,37910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778097967
OL,3,CMcCann family MP wants suspect in
OL,4,CMadeleine's disappearance to face
OL,5,Ctrial in UK
OL,7,FBefore Brueckner's release last year,
OL,8,Fthe Metropolitan Police announced they
OL,9,Fhad sent an international letter of
OL,10,Frequest to interview him about
OL,11,FMadeleine's disappearance, which he
OL,12,Frefused.
OL,14,FITV News has previously spoken to one
OL,15,Fof Brueckner's former associates,
OL,16,FHelge Buschung, who suggested he was
OL,17,Finvolved in the kidnapping.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
